# Zoo LinkedList

A singly linked list implementation that stores Animal objects in Java.

## What it does

Manages a zoo of animals using a custom linked list.
Supports adding animals to the front or back of the list,
removing from the front, and printing all animals with their details.

## Concepts covered

- Enums (Category, Diet)
- Classes and constructors
- Singly linked list (AddHead, AddTail, RemoveHead)
- Object composition